General.Name: Golden Ocean Group Ltd
General.Description: Golden Ocean Group Limited, a shipping company, owns and operates a fleet of dry bulk vessels worldwide. Its dry bulk vessels consist of Newcastlemax, Capesize, Kamsarmax, and Panamax vessels operating in the spot and time charter markets. The company also transports various bulk commodities, including ores, coal, grains, and fertilizers. As of March 20, 2025, it owned a fleet of 83 dry bulk vessels. Golden Ocean Group Limited is based in Hamilton, Bermuda.
